name: steven humphreys
text: I haven't been there in years so this may be incorrect information nowadays.  Great shop with good coral selection, excellent employee knowledge, top of the line products, etc.   3 stars because coral frag prices aren't labeled in the frag runs.  Change that and it's a 5 star shop, easy.

name: Chad kiper
text: The best! I've been dealing with Rich for probably 25+ years.  Quality advice, knowledge and products. A+

name: Michael Tomlinson
text: Again drove all the way from Biloxi to progressive marine for the second time , arrived at 2:30 and no one there and shop has been emptied out. Don't know if they moved or went out of business. Probably the later considering you must have to have an appointment to get in. Fool me once shame on you fool me twice shame on me. Won't get a chance to get me again, I won't go back.

name: Gerald Grant
text: Stopped by there yesterday and got 3 frags on my way home,  wonderful selection,  enjoyed talking to owner  Rich.. wil be back again when in town.  Thx

name: Lee Lane
text: Cool people who really know their stuff! A great place for coral, fish, equipment, and information.

name: Brian steele
text: Awesome place great stuff for your salt water tanks friendly staff

name: Steven
text: Like to stop in and see the section every so often
